sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User / Browser
    participant R as React HomePage
    participant S as fetch service
    participant V as Vite proxy :5173 default
    participant K as uvicorn :8000
    participant F as FastAPI router
    participant P as Pydantic
    participant O as SQLAlchemy
    participant DB as PostgreSQL :5432 default

    U->>R: click "Call backend API"
    R->>S: sendSampleEndpointRequest(bodyText)
    S->>V: POST /api/sample-endpoint, JSON, 3s timeout
    V->>K: forward POST /api/sample-endpoint
    K->>F: route to create_sample()
    F->>P: validate request body
    alt invalid body
        P-->>F: ValidationError
        F-->>K: 422 Unprocessable Entity
    else valid body
        P-->>F: SampleRequest foo, baz
        F->>O: open session via get_db_session
        O->>DB: SELECT from sample_data
        DB-->>O: rows
        O-->>F: SampleData list
        F-->>K: 200 SampleResponse message, baz, sample_data
    end
    K-->>V: HTTP response
    V-->>S: HTTP response
    S->>S: parse JSON or handle timeout
    S-->>R: SampleEndpointResult
    R->>R: formatApiResult(ok, status, data)
    R-->>U: render request and response boxes
